## 2026-04-03 - No unused token detection anywhere in the product
- Implemented two surfaces for unused token detection (tokens with zero Figma usage AND no alias dependents):
  1. **AnalyticsPanel "Unused Tokens" section** (Ship > Validation tab): collapsible section showing count + scrollable list of unused tokens with path, type, and set. Shows a notice when no Figma usage data is available. Clicking a token navigates to it in the token list.
  2. **`has:unused` search qualifier** in TokenList search: users can type `has:unused` in the search bar to filter to unused tokens only. Follows the same pattern as `has:duplicate`, `has:generated`, etc.
